    <description>Object that maps the GL Accounts to Codes
Stores the mapping of the chart of Account and different transaction. 
Receivable Codes relates to the invoice type debit codes, 
Income code relates to invoice line credit codes, 
Payable codes relates to payable type credit codes and 
Expense Code relates to payable line debit codes. 
Users can link the associated chart of accounts for different types of transactions under teh relevant GL account codes.
Population Requirement Details: The system automatically generates the &#39;GL Account Codes&#39; on creation of the Accounting Profile in the system and each of these accounts can be seamlessly linked to the Chart of Accounts. Only the mapping exercise need to be performed.
[MODULE: Accounting]
[LOAD: Optional]
[PREREQUISITES: Chart of Accounts, Accounting Profile]
[REPLACEMENT OBJECT API: NA]
[COMMENTS: NA]</description>
